Aim:
To write a program using Pandas to create and display a DataFrame and use Matplotlib to plot the data.

Algorithm:
Step 1 - Start
Step 2 - Import pandas as pd and matplotlib.pyplot as plt.
Step 3 - Create two lists: Points and Teams.
Step 4 - Create a DataFrame using pd.DataFrame() with columns Points and Teams.
Step 5 - Print the DataFrame.
Step 6 - Plot Name on the x-axis and SL on the y-axis using plt.plot().
Step 7 - Add title and axis labels.
Step 8 - Display the plot using plt.show().
Step 9 - Stop
